# Full environment contract: ../../.cursor/specs/notify.md
#
# Comma-separated domains allowed to sign up. Empty or omit = no domain check (local dev).
# ALLOWED_EMAIL_DOMAINS=acme.com,acme.org
#
# SMTP (Nodemailer) — example values are for Resend; swap host/user for Gmail, Postmark, etc.
# SMTP_HOST=smtp.resend.com
# SMTP_PORT=465
# SMTP_USER=resend
# SMTP_PASS=re_xxxxxxxx
# SMTP_FROM=onboarding@yourverifieddomain.com
